seo: FastJSON漏洞,DNSLog检测,反连扫描,网站漏洞
seo_en: FastJSON vulnerability,DNSLog detection,reverse connection scanning,website vulnerability
summary: 该插件通过DNSLog反连扫描网站是否存在FastJSON漏洞，检测目标是否可能受到远程命令执行攻击（RCE）影响。
summary_en: This plugin scans websites for FastJSON vulnerabilities using DNSLog reverse connections and detects whether the target is potentially vulnerable to remote command execution (RCE) attacks.
